---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Дарения">
    <div class="bg-orange-50 py-12">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-4">
                Подкрепете нашата кауза
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">
                Всяко дарение, независимо от размера му, ни помага да спасяваме
                животи, да осигуряваме храна, подслон и медицински грижи за
                животните в нужда.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 space-y-12">
        <!-- Bank Transfer -->
        <section
            class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100"
        >
            <h2
                class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center"
            >
                <svg
                    class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-700 mr-3"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a3 3 0 003-3V8a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 003 3z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>
                Банков превод
            </h2>
            <div
                class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm sm:text-base space-y-3"
            >
                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 border-b border-slate-200 pb-3"
                >
                    <span class="text-slate-700">Банка:</span>
                    <span class="sm:col-span-2 font-medium"
                        >Първа инвестиционна банка (Fibank)</span
                    >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 border-b border-slate-200 pb-3"
                >
                    <span class="text-slate-700">Титуляр:</span>
                    <span class="sm:col-span-2 font-medium"
                        >Фондация "Анимал Хоуп Варна"</span
                    >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 border-b border-slate-200 pb-3"
                >
                    <span class="text-slate-700">IBAN:</span>
                    <span class="sm:col-span-2 font-medium text-orange-700"
                        >BG56 FINV 9150 1215 7665 63</span
                    >
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2">
                    <span class="text-slate-700">BIC:</span>
                    <span class="sm:col-span-2 font-medium">FINV BGSF</span>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 pt-3 border-t border-slate-200 mt-3"
                >
                    <span class="text-slate-700">Основание:</span>
                    <span class="sm:col-span-2 font-medium"
                        >Дарение за дейността</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- PayPal -->
        <section
            class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100"
        >
            <h2
                class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center"
            >
                <svg
                    class="w-8 h-8 text-[#00457C] mr-3"
                    fill="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                    <path
                        d="M7.076 21.337H2.47a.641.641 0 0 1-.633-.74L4.944.901C5.026.382 5.474 0 5.998 0h7.46c2.57 0 4.578.543 5.69 1.81 1.01 1.15 1.304 2.42 1.012 4.287-.023.143-.047.288-.077.437-.983 5.05-4.349 6.797-8.647 6.797h-2.19c-.524 0-.968.382-1.05.9l-1.12 7.106zM6.924 1.488L4.015 19.85h2.19c.524 0 .968-.382 1.05-.9l1.12-7.106a1.494 1.494 0 0 1 1.472-1.262h2.19c3.42 0 6.079-1.39 6.845-5.32.023-.118.044-.236.064-.354.218-1.39.006-2.316-.628-3.04-1.114-1.272-3.21-1.637-5.918-1.637H6.924z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>
                PayPal
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
                Бърз и сигурен начин да дарите от цял свят чрез вашия PayPal
                акаунт или кредитна карта.
            </p>
            <a
                href="#"
                class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-[#00457C] text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-[#003666] transition-colors"
            >
                Дарете с PayPal
            </a>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-700">
                Имейл за директен превод: animalhope.varna@gmail.com
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- SMS Donation -->
        <section
            class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100"
        >
            <h2
                class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center"
            >
                <svg
                    class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-700 mr-3"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>
                DMS SMS Дарение
            </h2>
            <div
                class="bg-orange-50 border border-orange-100 p-6 rounded-xl text-center"
            >
                <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 mb-2">Изпратете SMS с текст</p>
                <div
                    class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-orange-700 tracking-wider mb-2"
                >
                    DMS ANIMAL
                </div>
                <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 mb-4">на номер</p>
                <div
                    class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-wider mb-6"
                >
                    17 777
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">
                    Дари със SMS от 1,02 EUR/ 2 лв. Aбонирай се за месечно SMS дарение от 2,56 EUR или 5.11 EUR/ 5 или 10 лв.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Econt -->
        <section
            class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100"
        >
            <h2
                class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center"
            >
                <svg
                    class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600 mr-3"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>
                Еконт
            </h2>
            <div
                class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm sm:text-base space-y-3"
            >
                <p class="text-slate-700">
                    Можете да изпратите дарение чрез всеки офис на Еконт до:
                </p>
                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 border-b border-slate-200 pb-3 mt-3"
                >
                    <span class="text-slate-700">Получател:</span>
                    <span class="sm:col-span-2 font-medium"
                        >Фондация "Анимал Хоуп Варна"</span
                    >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 border-b border-slate-200 pb-3"
                >
                    <span class="text-slate-700">Телефон:</span>
                    <span class="sm:col-span-2 font-medium">087 6570311</span>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 pt-3 border-t border-slate-200 mt-3"
                >
                    <span class="text-slate-700">Офис:</span>
                    <span class="sm:col-span-2 font-medium"
                        >Моля, свържете се с нас за актуален офис</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Material Donations -->
        <section
            class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100"
        >
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
                Материални дарения
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
                Винаги имаме нужда от качествена храна (гранули и консерви),
                обезпаразитяващи препарати, медикаменти, каишки, поводи и
                постелки.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-600">
                Можете да донесете своите дарения всяка неделя на нашата среща
                пред Катедралата или да се свържете с нас, за да уточним как да
                ги предадете.
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>
